summary: OpenAI is hosting its first developer conference, OpenAI DevDay, on November 6, 2023, in San Francisco. The event will provide developers with a preview of new tools and an opportunity to exchange ideas with the OpenAI team. In-person attendees can also participate in breakout sessions led by OpenAI's technical staff. The conference aims to showcase the latest advancements in AI and enable developers to build new applications and services. Interested individuals can visit devday.openai.com to learn more and sign up for notifications about registration. Press inquiries can be directed to devdaypress@openai.com.
